{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"057a86ae45","title":"关于右派分子反动刊物“广场”主编张元勋的若干材料","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1e52a3e92","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"057a86ae45"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"40bc9a197e","name":"争鸣社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1f125a68f3","type":"title","text":"关于右派分子反动刊物“广场”主编张元勋的若干材料","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"75c9c4897a","type":"authors","text":"北京大学争鸣社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"a5c4d5609f","type":"paragraph","text":"编者按：自从党展开整风以来，群众积极性很高，都愿意助党整风除三害。可是，也有一些右派分子借此机会展开了反党反社会主义的活动。张元勋所写的“是时候了”，便是校内右派分子向党进攻的誓师辞。他们认为时机已到，纷纷抛出了充满咒骂与诽谤的陈腐滥调，相互配合地向党作猖狂进攻，否定肃反，咒骂党员，认为社会主义没有民主、自由……。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2999b7d08f","type":"paragraph","text":"作为“广场”主编的张元勋，以“诗人”身份出现，以诗作为武器向党作猖狂进攻。不过，他与其它露骨的右派分子不一样，侭管有时也免不了暴露他的本来面目，可是他却以隐蔽的形式出现。不看他整个的言行而只听他的一二句话，那么可能会被他迷惑。此外，张元勋很会运用两面派的手法。对这种人，更需要警惕!因为其恶毒更甚。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d3a7f2f6d5","type":"paragraph","text":"这里刊录的只是他的言行的一部分，而且还是比较初期的。最近，他的反党反社会主义的活动更形变本加厉。但从这些言行中我们已经可以看出张元勋这个“新人”的本来面目了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"f954b5f6bb","type":"subtitle","text":"一、主办“广场”，作反党反社会主义的喉舌","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"dccbf8df72","type":"subtitle","text":"A．“广场”的宗旨","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"359d467ca3","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“百花学社开会时邀请我参加，我决定参加，斗争是无期的，我们要联合起来。”(张对班上同学汪淅成的谈话)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"75d61fe486","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“我为什么要办‘广场’呢?因为没有刊物不好说话，有了刊物好讲话，可以向他们(指党)开开炮！”(同上)(按：运用大字报形式咒骂党还不够，还要集合起来有组织地攻击党。)并且，“‘广场’有其鲜明的倾向性，绝不登卫道者的文章(按：卫道者是指马克思主义者，这是整风运动开始后，右派分子对于卫马克思主义者的通称)，要登非正统的文章”(按：可见“广场”的宗旨)(在百花学社第二次大会上张的发言)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"9bd4cd751e","type":"subtitle","text":"B．纠集同伙、筹划经费和物质材料","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d652cf0fea","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“‘广场’编委中叶于生最有办法，他是调干，年纪大作事不象我这样轻率，他思考问题深入。”(六月二十日张的发言)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"8cba90114b","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“我们要去找孔厥寻求物质上和精神上的支持。”(张对文三(1)班一同学说)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"0540aaba1d","type":"paragraph","text":"3．找马校长募集经费，对马老说：“党委负责同志已同意我们办一学生刊物。”(按：本来大骂党委，这里却要盗用党委名义。张元勋骂“党委无耻”，倒底无耻是谁呢?!)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"60ed5e85b9","type":"paragraph","text":"4．6月6日“广场”主编张元勋派崔德甫等赴前门文化用品批发站说：“我们学生会要纸，因为要印学习材料，为了整风，所以这是急切要用的。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"75f6d62ced","type":"paragraph","text":"5．6月7日张主编亲至批发站说：“我们的材料要送印刷厂了。纸，因为学生经费不够，只要十六令。”发票上款开的是“北京大学”。(按：前盗用党委同志名义，这儿又盗用学生会名义，真好手法!!)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"94ff60a4ba","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“广场”因其反社会主义内容所以，工人不印，张大叫“今天不能出，明天出；明天不能出，后天出；我不能出，我儿子出；我儿子不能出，我孙子出。”并高呼“‘广场’不朽！‘广场’万岁!”(在宿舍)(按：“广场”倒底有些什么内容值得张如此坚持要出呢?并且如此富有“英雄气概”呢?张还说“我负‘广场’一切责任，不管是法律的或是政治上。”看来，却原来是它的反党反社会主义的内容。)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"604e8979ef","type":"subtitle","text":"C．“广场”的阴暗底细","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d5386870a7","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“我想退出‘广场’，七个编委又不让退，他们怕我揭开内部黑幕。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"318bb24ce8","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“‘广场’大权在我手里，我们可以决定一切，我可以退出，揭发他们的阴私”(张对班上一同学的说话)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"ceeab28a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“‘广场’第二次编委会上，谭天荣与刘奇弟都出席了。他们都想加入编委会，大家争吵得很厉害，但为了长远的利益，谭和刘也让步了。”(6月25日在班会上张的说话)(按：是什么样的“长远的利益”，以致使谭和刘也让了步，而互相分工，配合起来。“广场”倒底有什么阴私，既不能有一人暴露，如果是光明磊落的事，为什么不能公开。可见张元勋所说的“‘广场’在我手里绝不会变质”的“质”所包含的意义了。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"1bb10ef5bb","type":"subtitle","text":"二、对社会主义民主、自由的迂回进攻、否定肃反运动，攻击党团","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d0f95a87c1","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“我至今仍认为民主是目的，假若民主是手段的话，那末社会主义建成了，民主也没有了。同样，我认为自由也是目的。”(6月25日在班会上张的发言)(按：又是一次玩弄手法，其实着重点在后面：否认社会主义的民主自由。前面第一句话，如果不是故意，也是冀图混淆民主这个概念，因为民主是目的，那么，资产阶级社会不用推翻，因为亦有“民主”，可见张元勋所追求的是什么!)","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"184a77add9","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“到校后，你入了团","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"473a1299ee","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"f6d2be85cf","type":"paragraph","text":"你竟少了一半笑意","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b4c70db7ed","type":"paragraph","text":"轻了一半歌声","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"baeaef206a","type":"paragraph","text":"不久，听说你又入了党","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"8bd894c5e1","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2417ca842f","type":"paragraph","text":"但从此再不见你的笑意","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d919da12b2","type":"paragraph","text":"听不见你的歌声","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"de14db62c7","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d71fa0d5a1","type":"paragraph","text":"你伸过来冰凉的手","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"af2d37d2d2","type":"paragraph","text":"你投来冰冷的目光","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"9e21336608","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"c7a8eaa367","type":"paragraph","text":"我几乎辨不出你的嗓子了","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"fc001a4ea1","type":"paragraph","text":"你喉咙里响着别人的声音","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"333098212a","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"72d2b7dcea","type":"paragraph","text":"悲哀啊，朋友","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"599ad4fb20","type":"paragraph","text":"我为你伤心地哭泣","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"70fc527245","type":"paragraph","text":"哀悼你死得过早的青春","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d3ec21b485","type":"paragraph","text":"(中略)","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"a5db870549","type":"paragraph","text":"你得意洋洋地走进坟墓","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"7bcd4cf46b","type":"paragraph","text":"躺在那儿安安稳稳","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"100b24d9ac","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"ff3d705510","type":"paragraph","text":"盖在你坟上的泥土","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b1a4f2fd00","type":"paragraph","text":"是纸纸辉煌的“功勋”","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e5a41e8a62","type":"paragraph","text":"长在你坟上的花草","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"a3cb4b3434","type":"paragraph","text":"是片片谄媚的歌声","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"835f516c9a","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"7315c0d199","type":"paragraph","text":"愿我的诗象一支号角","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"41756c6330","type":"paragraph","text":"引着你去寻找","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e43840bc93","type":"paragraph","text":"失掉了的青春","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e0db1199b9","type":"paragraph","text":"(墓志铭)","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b53bceb471","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：张元勋用他歪曲了的党团员的形象来影射整个党团、肆意对党团进行恶毒的污蔑与谩骂，想把党团员都从革命队伍里拉出来，跟着他走向“民主个人主义”的王国中去寻找“青春”)","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"a6a3179605","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“只因为你正直，开朗","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"910a7290c7","type":"paragraph","text":"不爱把应说的话放在心底埋藏","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b69ce7c7b4","type":"paragraph","text":"你不会在某些人的耳边日夜轻唱","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"67e94b7163","type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"7e0ce31d98","type":"paragraph","text":"你更不会颠倒是非忘却了良心","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"5b24ca5839","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"080f2f1f5e","type":"paragraph","text":"偏见与恶意，嫉妒与诽谤","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6c183b9466","type":"paragraph","text":"怀着不可告人的个人欲望","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6f69124a98","type":"paragraph","text":"把别人的身体当作向上爬的梯子","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"01868c7f46","type":"paragraph","text":"把无耻巨足践踏着别人的脊梁","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"c464608cbf","type":"paragraph","text":"步步直上……","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e9b2b3b05a","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"734fb48f7e","type":"paragraph","text":"从此，便有一只恶毒的巨足踏着你的背上","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"48de7f3c25","type":"paragraph","text":"从此，你便俯首无言度着奴隶式的时光","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"cafbf65182","type":"paragraph","text":"而从此你更失掉了天赋的权利","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d67bb82f96","type":"paragraph","text":"你不敢为自己的遭遇哭泣","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2d904a2784","type":"paragraph","text":"你的眼泪只能在深夜里偷落在脸上","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"295e23be02","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6b16a37250","type":"paragraph","text":"我太痴信那些老爷式的党员了","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"bc0b100952","type":"paragraph","text":"我与他们一起骂你是“反革命分子”与“黑帮”","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"40d0c4a8cd","type":"paragraph","text":"(兄弟，听我说)","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"435e2950bf","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：肃反运动中，一个同学因思想反动，曾被批判，但党组织并未说该人是反革命分子，当时张元勋却以积极分子姿态出现，说该人是反革命分子，这首诗中却说：“我太痴信那些老爷式的党员了”。把责任推到党员身上引起那个人对党的仇恨，造谣污蔑并企图以此拉拢该人及少数别有用心的人。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"791eb0ddd9","type":"paragraph","text":"张所描写的情况与事实不符，他恶毒地夸大了个别错误以达到反党的目的。他把党描写成世界上最丑恶的、最无耻的，可见他对党怀着多大刻骨的仇恨；他把思想反动的人描写成正直、善良、开朗、不会拍“马屁”的好人，可见张之反动立场是十分明确的。)","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6c719d6cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“这个运动已远远地超过了党内的整风的范围，而具有了伟大的社会思想意识大变革的巨大意义!人与人之间的关系要重新调整；一些过去习以为常的正面的与反面的东西，要重新进行肯定与否定；对于现代的论点与观点要重新估订、评价与探索。”(张元勋执笔的“广场”发刊词)(按：张元勋这里所指的是要进行整个社会大变革，从思想意识、人们关系一直到国际上一切论点与观点均要重新调整。他的意思如果不是否定社会主义社会的一切也是要否定社会主义中的指导思想与人们间的关系，实际上就是要消灭社会主义。可见，张元勋要主办“广场”的宗旨是如何明确，这些是他运用任何两面派手法所不能掩饰的)。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"beb1d91167","type":"subtitle","text":"三、口是心非，耍两面派手法","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"ded50f71e3","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“我可能被坏分子利用，他们让我到校外宣传。”(5月24日张元勋与曹某说)(按：五月二十六日他就欣然到清华去点火了)。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2181694efa","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“我真不知道‘广场’，后果怎样?我很可能被反革命分子利用。”(对文三(2)班一同学说)","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"41ad908453","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“‘广场’是为了追求真理，什么是真理呢?那就是马克思列宁主义!”(“救救孩子!”)(按：张元勋侭管他不要马列主义，但是为了“广场”，为了其反社会主义的目的时，就抬出马克思列宁主义，以取得群众的捐款，达到“广场”的出版。这种手法在张元勋那里已经屡见不鲜了，如先后盗用党委负责同志、学生会名义等等。)","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e1127f667f","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“‘广场’在我手里不会变质。”“‘广场’万岁!”“‘广场’绝不登反社会主义言论。”(6月19日“控诉”印刷一厂工人大会张的发言)(按：看一下“广场”的目录就可以知道这种论调已经无耻到什么地步!)。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"7d3b3949e1","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“侭管我的姓名上","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"97527248b2","type":"paragraph","text":"还蒙上了一层‘右派’的暗影","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"5c678accd6","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上却没有一种力量能动摇我爱党的心","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"09ef559b76","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"db4c9f40b4","type":"paragraph","text":"我对党犯下了痛心的错误","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"869d0c6f0e","type":"paragraph","text":"我无意中把母亲刺伤。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"566b7e4f02","type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我流着悔改的眼泪","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"09cd94ed84","type":"paragraph","text":"低头跪在母亲的身旁”。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"4bbb8b3648","type":"paragraph","text":"(“我以公民的心，警告你”)","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6065e9ef7d","type":"paragraph","text":"按：他说他无意地刺伤了母亲，从上述事实看来，显然他是有意地，并且是凶狠地、恶毒地。他还企图否认自己是右派。“诗人”又在耍花招了，不过，虚伪的诗句掩盖不了真实。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b091c43017","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“认错与悔改，我是向着真理和党的。对于任何个人，我无半个柔和的音符为他轻歌(“自认及其他”)","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"78c6911205","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：张元勋在“悔恨”自己的错误时，总是抬出真理和党来，但是在他那里，可以看出，党是抽象的，并不是全体党员组成的；这样，他的认错与悔改也就没有任何根据了。而且对“广场”内幕的百般抵赖。能看出他有半点悔恨的真诚么?)","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2c508b9def","type":"subtitle","text":"四、诱胁同伙，继续抗拒","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"c99e2e3cae","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“‘广场’文章的作者能够大胆地写，这应当谅解。不应考察他们的动机……”","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6dec846dc5","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“为什么要和谭天荣划清界限?他的文章只是词句激烈一些，我看不出有什么反社会主义的地方。”(在“控诉”印刷一厂工人大会之后，张在大饭厅门口一高橙子上的说话)(按：真是“物以类聚”，张怎能看到谭的反社会主义言行呢?!既然是同伙，当然应该臭气相投了。)","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"8ff8ac1472","type":"paragraph","text":"3．在党委第一书记江隆基同志批判右派兴风作浪后，杨路写了大字报与之对抗，张元勋在杨路大字报后面写：","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"90801e3c78","type":"paragraph","text":"“杨路，你要小心，有人说你过几天骨头就软了。三年也不会软，你们还要搞一次肃反吧!”","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"6fdeb8c3cb","type":"paragraph","text":"4．在中文系文三(1)班批判沈泽宜的大字报后面，张元勋作了批语：","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"b666d20108","type":"paragraph","text":"“你把他骂成小丑，或是你割下他的头","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"ff18558942","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，他的心灵依旧存在，","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"0a6f694cd5","type":"paragraph","text":"他的傲然的素质","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e408298543","type":"paragraph","text":"决不会因为你们的诽谤而消失而无有","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e386a53574","type":"paragraph","text":"请先别庆祝你们的丰收。","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"ffafc1228d","type":"paragraph","text":"爱我者，我报以叹息。","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"91ab90b0bb","type":"paragraph","text":"恨我者，我报以微笑。","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"60f5ad3c66","type":"paragraph","text":"不论头上是怎样的天空","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"cd932683f3","type":"paragraph","text":"我准备承受一切风暴。","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"4731f74f9f","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：这里的含意是鼓励沈泽宜继续抗拒，维护“傲然的素质”；应该象他一样“坚定不移”。)","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"7909374aad","type":"paragraph","text":"5．沈泽宜写了“如果你还有爱我之情”后故作悔恨的姿态，张元勋写了下列的诗行：","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"c5e51cbea8","type":"paragraph","text":"但求你的乐声粗犷而深沉，","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"2d664de26e","type":"paragraph","text":"也不要先弹出欢乐的音阶，","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"e7ead292b5","type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你，歌手啊，我必须哭泣，","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"1b73a0a2cc","type":"paragraph","text":"不然，这沉重的心就要爆裂；","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"d68f251011","type":"paragraph","text":"因为它曾经为忧伤所哺育","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"95ea73d469","type":"paragraph","text":"如今他就要受到最痛的一击，","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"93e1a4e6e8","type":"paragraph","text":"使它立刻碎裂——或者皈依的歌唱；","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"1ad942d11d","type":"paragraph","text":"——张元勋引自拜伦","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"df1102b726","type":"paragraph","text":"诗给宜6．30","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"296bfdf9a8","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：张在这里明显地露出威胁之意，也在这里，“诗人”已变成狰狞的魔鬼了——这就是本来面目。)","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"031049fadf","type":"paragraph","text":"6．6月29日中文系召开批判张元勋大会，他却和陈奉孝(又一右派分子)到颐和园划船，回来洋洋得意说：“我这一天的任务完成了。”","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"1def5ca3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"(按：张元勋可见是怎样对待批评的，他目前更变本加厉。我们认为，如果他再坚持抗拒，那么，其后果是很清楚的，这一点，张元勋大概也会知道。)","index":123,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"9694d41377","type":"paragraph","text":" (陈汉时辑录)","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"},{"id":"3c39b477b8","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学“争鸣社”《论坛》第三期，1957年7月。","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45"}],"page":{"id":"de1116a8b4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"057a86ae45","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}